<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> cuntara pāṇṭiya tEvaṟku yā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> vatu <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaciṅka kulakāla
<lb n="2"/>vaḷanāṭṭu kuḷamaṅkala ṉāṭṭu cempāṭṭūrāṉa cempiyaṉ puttā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>mpūr Uṭaiyār tiruvaiyāṟu ṉāyanār kōyilil muppatu
<lb n="4"/>vaṭṭattu kāṇi Uṭaiya civappirāmaṇa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> Uṭaiya viḷakkukku kaikko
<lb n="5" break="no"/>koṇṭa nilaṅkacca ceyyu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ṇataṭi Iraṇṭum vaṭṭa
<lb n="6"/>kurukai paṟikālum Ilum <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ṉavāykkālum mēṭu
<lb n="7"/>taṭi Iraṇṭum Āka nila <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> Eṭṭu viḷa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>kkum cantiyātīpam cantirātitta <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
